dct_title_s: Sunmap tourist map Cairns and district: / Your official holiday guide, including the Mulgrave shire
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Relief shown by shading. "© Crown copyright reserved, printed August 1993." Ancillary maps: district map, towns of Edmonton, Gordonvale, Babinda, Aloomba, Miriwinni, Bellenden Ker, Bramston Beach, all at scale 1:25000. Includes illustrations, advertisements, text and index.
